Package: d6
Title: Simplify Workflows of D6 Research Projects
Version: 0.1.0.0
Date: 2020-10-01
Authors@R: "Cedric Scherer <cedricphilippscherer@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: The goal of the d6 package is to simplify the project workflow within the department “Ecologcial Dynamics” at the Leibniz Institute for Zoo and Wildlife Research by providing a standardized folder structure, templates for reports and utility functions.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: CC0
LazyData: true
